1.2
log
@Update freeimage to 3.15.2, including many SECURITY fixes to the included image
libraries.  Also respect CC, CXX, CFLAGS and CXXFLAGS, get rid of ^M line
endings in the patch and fix "make regress".

ok eric@@ (maintainer)
